description: Whip up this easy omelette recipe for breakfast, lunch or dinner. Made with eggs, potatoes and red onion, this is sure to become a new family favourite.
name: 3-ingredient Omelette Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Invert omelette onto a large plate, then slide omelette back into pan and cook for 2 minutes or until golden and set. Slide omelette onto plate. Top with salad leaves, slice and serve.
